snippet.textDisplay: So beautiful! I will NEVER get tired of this song or video, but when will my heart stop hurting while watching or listening to him... watching always brings tears to my eyes and a lump in my throat. Gone too soon... I miss him! George Michael (since the Wham! days) is my all time favorite singer. Wham!'s music, and positive message "Choose Life," helped me get through my tough teenage years, and for that I will always be thankful to them. There has never been, nor will there ever be again, a voice as beautiful as George's voice. I miss being able to hear new songs from him. Thank goodness there's youtube where I can look up all of the wonderful songs/videos/concert clips, and interviews, he was apart of since the 1980's. I guess like my mother who has missed Elvis for many, many years, I will always miss George Michael. I hope when I get to Heaven one day I see George standing next to Elvis leading the Heavenly choir. :) <3
